description:
Need a replacement blade? Need to cut more soft wood than you expected? Either way, this medium tooth blade for Silky’s Gomboy 240 saw is engineered to efficiently cut soft woods. The blade’s hard chrome plating resists the effects of tree resin and easily wipes clean.

  • Rust-resistant, taper-ground blade is SK-4 high carbon steel
  • Steel is hard chrome plated to resist the effects of tree resin and wipe clean easily
  • Impulse-hardened, non-set teeth for cutting efficiency
  • 10 teeth per 3cm work well for cutting soft wood
name: Silky Gomboy 240 Spare Blade - Medium Tooth
